HPC Challenge Benchmark: HPL

Usage:
	
    a) x10c -d directoryForGeneratedFiles -BAD_PLACE_RUNTIME_CHECK=false PLU2_C.x10
	* directoryForGeneratedFiles contains the generated .class and .java files;
	* add other x10c flags if necessary 

    b) Make ( optional if people want to use the C BLAS library)
	* update the locations of required libraries beforehand
		
    c) x10 -classpath directoryForGeneratedfiles -NUMBER_OF_LOCAL_PLACES=1 
	-INIT_THREADS_PER_PLACE=ttt lu.PLU2_C N b px py [C_Mode] [verify] [libraryFileName]
        * ttt should be equal to (px*py+1) 
        * add other x10 flags if necessary 
